        <abstract>
            <p>Glad to hear Wallace is contender for Gold Medal. Has highest esteem for his extraordinary talents.</p>
            <p>Thanks for H. Barkly’s letter from Mauritius.</p> 
<p>Glad to see HB takes same view as CD about bones of deer [see <hi rend="doubleUnderline">5395</hi>].</p> 
            <p>Objections to continental extension theory.</p> 
<p>Progress [on <hi rend="italic">Variation</hi>] very slow.</p> 
        </abstract>
